ANALYSIS   Combining following three data, a final value for the
           partial cross section of the 7Be(n,p0) reaction at
           thermal energy was obtained.
           The main measurement:
            43500 +/- 700(ERR-S) +/- 1700(ERR-SYS) b.
           Two additional comparative measurements:
            3mm of 6LiF standard
             44900 +/- 1100(ERR-S) +/- 3500(ERR-SYS) b.
            20mm of 6LiF standard
             43500 +/- 700(ERR-S) +/- 1700(ERR-SYS) b.
COMMENT    The final value combining three data for 7Be(n,p0)
           mentioned as 43600 +/- 1600 b is typo. The value 43800
           +/- 1400b mentioned both in last part in the main text
           and in the abstract is correct. (confirmed by author)
